txt.en: Supplies and rations can be found at Dâr Mauzur.\n\nYou should destroy supplies and collect rations.
'I thank you for these rations, [placeholder]. I am looking at what you have brought here and it seems good taste is not to be paired with much of the food to be found in Mordor.'
Bregdal can be found on the border of Talath Úrui and Dor Amarth.\n\nYou should speak with Bregdal.
Dâr Mauzur is sparsely populated with many who served under Ugrukhôr before the fall of Sauron.
Supplies and rations can be found at Dâr Mauzur.\n\nYou should destroy supplies and collect rations.
Destroy supplies and collect rations at Dâr Mauzur

Many supplies and rations are still scattered in every corner of Dâr Mauzur. While some of the rations are vile Orkish foods, others were meant for the evil men under Sauron's command and may be more palatable. You decide to search for any rations that the men of Gondor might stomach.
